CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 9, 1946, pg. 20 reads: " Fun And Frolic - Little Billy Strange of Webster Avenue was guest of honor at a gay frolic in honor of his birthday last week. Pictured at the party are, left to right: Sonny Taylor, Edward Woods, the honoree; Richard Reed and Barbara Taylor. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Sonny Taylor, Edward Woods, Billy Strange standing behind his birthday cake, Richard Reed, and Barbara Taylor blowing out candles in Strange home, Webster Avenue, Hill District
